<div class="post"><div class="posttop"><div class="username">Maledict</div><div class="date">March 3rd, 2007, 05:28 AM</div></div><div class="posttext">No, its a huge difference. I don't know about you, but I'm already almost done casting the next Frost Bolt by the time the Frostbite proc will even show up. The people suggesting you always Alternate between FB and Ice Lance aren't calculating in.<br />
