I don't think you understand mate. <br />
<br />
When frostbite procs, you're right - you're half way through asting your frostbolt. Continue casting the frostbolt. As *soon* as you finish casting it, hit the ice lance key - literally hammer it. You will cast the frostbolt and the ice lance att he same time, and both will hit the target att he same time and count as hitting a frozen target. You don't need to stop casting or anything - there's absolutely no break in rythym required in any way, it's a seamless cast sequence.</div></div><hr />


