<div class="post"><div class="posttop"><div class="username">Maledict</div><div class="date">March 3rd, 2007, 07:38 AM</div></div><div class="posttext">And this doesnt change anything about ice lance mages in PvE soloing - absolutely nothing at all. I've *neveR* ever had an ice lance crit NOT break frostbite / frost nova in PvP since I started combining it with the frostbolt trick outlined earlier. <br />
