In group play, yes it does lower it's power - but I have to be completely honest, what sort of groups are people playing with where a frostbite proc isn't instantly consumed instantly by your other group members anyway? I know when I was specced that way, I'd be lucky enough to get one ice lance off in an instance run in time. (POssibility - I always run with windfurying shaman, which means the mobs taking tons and tons of melee hits very very fast, which makes it break a lot easler than if you didnt have a shaman).<br />
